Deployment flow chart
                ┌─────────────────────┐
                │   feature branch    │
                │ feature/anything    │
                └─────────┬───────────┘
                          │
                          │ commit + push
                          ▼
                ┌─────────────────────┐
                │   GitHub stores it  │
                │  nothing deploys    │
                └─────────┬───────────┘
                          │
                          │ merge into staging
                          ▼
                ┌─────────────────────┐
                │      staging        │
                │   test branch       │
                └─────────┬───────────┘
                          │
                          │ push / merge
                          ▼
                ┌─────────────────────┐
                │  GitHub Action runs │
                │ updates gh-pages    │
                │ inside /staging/    │
                └─────────┬───────────┘
                          │
                          ▼
                ┌─────────────────────┐
                │ staging website     │
                │ /staging/           │
                └─────────┬───────────┘
                          │
                          │ test everything
                          │ if okay
                          ▼
                ┌─────────────────────┐
                │ merge staging into  │
                │       main          │
                └─────────┬───────────┘
                          │
                          │ push / merge
                          ▼
                ┌─────────────────────┐
                │  GitHub Action runs │
                │ updates gh-pages    │
                │ root production     │
                └─────────┬───────────┘
                          │
                          ▼
                ┌─────────────────────┐
                │ production website  │
                │        /            │
                └─────────────────────┘


What each branch means

feature/*   = work safely, nothing public changes
staging     = test deployment
main        = production deployment
gh-pages    = final published site only


Super simple memory rule

push feature  -> no deployment
push staging  -> staging site updates
push main     -> production site updates


