Daily workflow chart

Start work
   │
   ▼
Create feature branch from staging
   │
   ▼
Make changes in VS Code
   │
   ▼
Commit + push feature branch
   │
   ▼
Merge feature -> staging
   │
   ▼
Test on /staging/
   │
   ├── if broken -> fix in feature/staging and test again
   │
   └── if okay
         ▼
      Merge staging -> main
         │
         ▼
      Live site updates



One-line version
feature -> staging -> main -> gh-pages -> live

Best shortcut to remember
feature = build
staging = test
main    = release
gh-pages = serve